# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# x402 Server — Environment Variables for Integration Tests
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#
#   cp x402-server/.env.example x402-server/.env
#
# ⚠️  NEVER share or commit your private key — .env is already in .gitignore.
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# EVM_PRIVATE_KEY
#   Required only for the "pay & fetch" integration tests (group 4).
#   Use a TESTNET wallet only — NEVER paste a mainnet key.
#
#   How to get a testnet wallet + USDC:
#     1. Generate a fresh keypair (Foundry — https://getfoundry.sh):
#          npx cast w new
#        Or export a private key from MetaMask / any EVM wallet.
#
#     2. Fund it with free testnet USDC on Base Sepolia:
#          https://portal.cdp.coinbase.com/products/faucet
#          Network: Base Sepolia  |  Token: USDC
#          (You need at least $0.012 USDC to cover all 5 test endpoints.)
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

EVM_PRIVATE_KEY=0xYOUR_TESTNET_PRIVATE_KEY_HERE

# Optional: point the tests at a specific server URL (default: spun up in-process)
# X402_SERVER_URL=https://your-server.up.railway.app
